 m_aMissionDescriptors {
  CRF_MissionDescriptor "{644250503DF684C0}" {
   m_sTitle "Mission: Situation"
   m_sTextData "The discovery of the location of a famous Pharaoh's missing tomb has caught the attention of a number of competing treasure hunter groups. They each desire to claim the Pharaoh's mummy, for ill or for good. They would sabotage each other at the earliest opportunity if not for the rumors that the tomb is guarded by the ancient spirits of mighty warriors, pledged to the Pharaoh by a Coalition of his loyal vassals..."\
   ""\
   "BLUFOR Composition: 40x Bolt Action Infantry"\
   "BLUFOR Assets: Daring, fortune, and enterprising spirit"\
   ""\
   "INDFOR Composition: 60x Melee Infantry"\
   "INDFOR Assets: Loyalty, bravery, and ruthlessness"\
   ""\
   "Time: The peak of Khonsu's might"\
   ""\
   "Weather: Khonsu has cleared the way for all travelers in the night"
   m_aFactionKeys {
   }
   m_bShowForAnyFaction 1
  }
  CRF_MissionDescriptor "{64425051F2E00216}" {
   m_sTitle "BLUFOR Objectives"
   m_sTextData "This pyramid hides the tomb of a forgotten Pharaoh, and his mummy is a source of real power. We’re in a race with other treasure hunters who want it for all the wrong reasons. Rumor has it that the place is protected by the spirits of warriors sworn to guard him forever... Either way, we need to get in first, grab the mummy, and get out alive before the competition or the tomb itself finishes us."\
   ""\
   "Defeat the guardians"\
   "Claim the Pharaoh"\
   "Escape before the other treasure hunters can steal the Pharaoh"
   m_aFactionKeys +{
   }
   m_bShowForAnyFaction 0
  }
  CRF_MissionDescriptor "{64425051B9B5AF67}" {
   m_sTitle "CIV Objectives"
   m_sTextData "The living have found the path I ordered erased. They think my corpse a prize, not understanding how it has remained hidden for so long. My vassals stand watch, blessed by the Gods with strength, speed, and cunning. The intruders shall learn why some legacies are better left forgotten to the sands of time."
   m_aFactionKeys +{
   }
   m_bShowForAnyFaction 0
  }
  CRF_MissionDescriptor "{644250519BE30999}" {
   m_sTitle "INDFOR Objectives"
   m_sTextData "The living draw near, covetous of my ancient power. They come not as worshipers, but as thieves, seeking to wield my remains for their own ends. Remember your oaths, and let no unworthy trespasser enter my chamber. Stand fast and stand eternal, warriors of the Coalition, and remind these fools that the dead do not suffer the living."\
   ""\
   "Extinguish the torches"\
   "Use your night vision"\
   "Use your smoke"\
   "Protect the Pharaoh"\
   "Eliminate the intruders"
   m_aFactionKeys +{
   }
   m_bShowForAnyFaction 0
  }
  CRF_MissionDescriptor "{6442505149CF6C93}" {
   m_sTitle "Administration"
   m_sTextData "Do not use enemy equipment under any circumstances! A mummy wouldn't know how to use a gun, and a human can't steal a ghost's eyes..."
   m_aFactionKeys {
    "BLUFOR"
    "CIV"
    "INDFOR"
   }
   m_bShowForAnyFaction 0
  }
 }
